load("../../refinedata/analysis/analysis_total_Fixed.rda")
analysis_total<-analysis_total_Fixed

analysis_sido_day <- analysis_total %>% filter(  == '') %>% group_by() %>% summarise(` (hPa)` = mean(` (hPa)`,na.rm=TRUE))

ts <- ts(analysis_sido_day[-1]$` (hPa)`,frequency = 365, start = c(2016,1))

fit <- stl(ts, s.window = 'periodic')

par(mfrow=c(1,1))

plot(fit,
     main = '  (hPa)')
